extends ../../_layout

block vars
  - var pageTitle = 'Hello, world'
  - var pageDescription = "First post on this writing site. A few words on why I'm starting to write."
  - var pagePath = 'hello-world'
  - var bodyClass = 'thought-detail'
  - var date = '25 March 2026'

block content

  :markdown-it(html)

    This is the first post on this site.

    I built it because I think writing is one of the highest-leverage things a person can do — it forces clarity, creates durable proof of work, and compounds over time. Every post is an asset.

    I'm Roman Licursi. I'm a CS junior at UW-Madison, currently spending a semester in Prague. I care about systems, leverage, and building things that scale beyond the hours I put in.

    I'll write here about technology, career decisions, tools I'm building, and how I think about navigating the current moment in AI and software.

    No schedule. No theme. Just things worth writing down.
